msgid "Please install Git. Download from: https://git-scm.com/download/"
msgstr "Git을 설치해 주세요. 다운로드: https://git-scm.com/download/win"

#: C:\KAIHATSU\agentcli\src\uagent\checks.py:19
msgid ""
"Please install Git. Example: sudo apt install git (Ubuntu/Debian) or sudo "
"yum install git (CentOS/RHEL)"
msgstr ""
"Git을 설치해 주세요. 예: sudo apt install git (Ubuntu/Debian) 또는 sudo yum "
"install git (CentOS/RHEL)"

#: C:\KAIHATSU\agentcli\src\uagent\checks.py:22
msgid ""
"Please install Git. If using Homebrew: brew install git, or install Xcode "
"Command Line Tools: xcode-select --install"
msgstr ""
"Git을 설치해 주세요. Homebrew 사용 시: brew install git, 또는 Xcode Command "
"Line Tools 설치: xcode-select --install"

#: C:\KAIHATSU\agentcli\src\uagent\checks.py:24
#, fuzzy
msgid "Please install Git. See: https://git-scm.com/download/"
msgstr "Git을 설치해 주세요. 참고: https://git-scm.com/"

#: C:\KAIHATSU\agentcli\src\uagent\checks.py:25
msgid "[ERROR] Git is not installed."
msgstr "[ERROR] Git이 설치되어 있지 않습니다."

