"\n"
"번호 입력:"

#: C:\KAIHATSU\agentcli\src\uagent\util_tools.py:824
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Run this skill as a system-level instruction and keep it active in this "
"session?\n"
"\n"
"Name: %(name)s\n"
"Path: %(path)s\n"
"\n"
"Proceed? Enter y to run, or c to cancel."
msgstr ""
"이 스킬을 시스템 수준 지시로 실행하고 이 세션에서 활성 상태로 유지할까요?\n"
"\n"
"이름: %(name)s\n"
"경로: %(path)s\n"
"\n"
"계속할까요? 실행은 y, 취소는 c를 입력하세요."

#: C:\KAIHATSU\agentcli\src\uagent\util_tools.py:924
#, fuzzy, python-format
msgid ""
":clean will delete conversation log files (scheck_log_*.jsonl) from disk.\n"
"Log dir: %(dir)s\n"
"Rule: total user/assistant/tool messages excluding system <= %(threshold)d\n"
"Targets: %(n)d\n"
"\n"
"Proceed? Enter y to run, or c to cancel."
msgstr ""
"  :clean [N]            user/assistant/tool 메시지 수(system 제외)가 N 이하"
"인 대화 로그(scheck_log_*.jsonl)를 삭제합니다(기본값=10)"

